item.description:
@sinisoul wrote:

[quote=“t4, post:7, topic:445046”][quote author=sinisoul link=topic=547736.msg4017035#msg4017035 date=1339719826]

Great tutorial! I want to see that java guru again it looks sexy with your name :o

not to rain on anyone’s parade, but this thread doesn’t exemplify what makes a java guru as it has absolutely nothing to do with the language - it has more to do with the rs2 protocol.

just sent in a thread to try and get the two badges differentiated.
[/quote]
good, i also put a word in for the ruby cup for you[/quote]

Appreciate it. I think now that more people are getting badges, that java guru and RSPS guru should be separated especially if we want to promote more people actually researching into the game engine. I’d be cool to see more threads like this because I really can’t write a thread about everything I know in the client. Doubt I’ll get it by the way, on probation for awhile. Thbt.
